<section id="layout-ncol" class="level2">
<h2 class="anchored" data-anchor-id="layout-ncol"><code>layout-ncol</code></h2>
<p>Use the <code>layout-ncol</code> chunk option to organize output in columns, e.g., <code>layout-ncol: 2</code> for two tables side-by-side.</p>
<div>
<div class="sourceCode cell-code" id="cb1" style="background: #f1f3f5;"><pre class="sourceCode markdown code-with-copy"><code class="sourceCode markdown"><span id="cb1-1"><span class="in" style="color: #5E5E5E;">```{r}</span></span>
<span id="cb1-2"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;">#| tbl-cap: Two tables</span></span>
<span id="cb1-3"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;">#| tbl-subcap: ["mtcars", "Just cars"]</span></span>
<span id="cb1-4"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;">#| layout-ncol: 2</span></span>
<span id="cb1-5"></span>
<span id="cb1-6"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;">library</span>(knitr)</span>
<span id="cb1-7"></span>
<span id="cb1-8"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;"># table on the left</span></span>
<span id="cb1-9"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;">kable</span>(<span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;">head</span>(mtcars[, <span class="dv" style="color: #AD0000;">1</span><span class="sc" style="color: #5E5E5E;">:</span><span class="dv" style="color: #AD0000;">3</span>]))</span>
<span id="cb1-10"></span>
<span id="cb1-11"><span class="co" style="color: #5E5E5E;"># table on the right</span></span>
<span id="cb1-12"><span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;">kable</span>(<span class="fu" style="color: #4758AB;">head</span>(cars))</span>
<span id="cb1-13"><span class="in" style="color: #5E5E5E;">```</span></span></code></pre></div>
